<li><strong>
<a href= "http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=reboot&amp;apropos=0&amp;sektion=8&amp;format=html"> reboot, halt(8)</a></strong> 
- arr&ecirc;te et red&eacute;marre le syst&egrave;me.

<li><strong>
<a href= "http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=shutdown&amp;apropos=0&amp;sektion=8&amp;format=html"> shutdown(8)</a></strong> 
